<body>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>This application does not collect, store, or share any personal user data. All features are available without registration and do not access sensitive information.</p>
  <p>The app requests system permissions solely to display status data through widgets. These include access to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Device battery status</li>
    <li>Connected Bluetooth device charge</li>
    <li>Step count and activity tracking</li>
    <li>RAM and internal storage information</li>
    <li>Weather data and location (if enabled)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>No data is transmitted to third parties. All processing is done locally on the device. The app does not use advertising or third-party analytics.</p>
